Package org.ros.android.view.visualization.shape

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Shape
    A Shape is a OpenGlDrawable that has a Color and a Transform that is applied to the OpenGL matrix stack before drawing.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GoalShape
    Represents the robot's current goal pose.
    PoseShape
    Represents the pose that will be published.
    RobotShape
    Represents the robot.
    TriangleFanShape
    A Shape defined by vertices using OpenGl's GL_TRIANGLE_FAN method.
